Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_Deep_Ma: These Player Items are created in partnership with Evil Geniuses, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_Lucid_T: The dreamer's eyes are opened to a world of anguish.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Aby: When the Abyssal Horde comes, it will be Vrogros at the vanguard of the charge, eager to bend yet another new land to his vile will.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Age: As the lone Protector's path takes him ever further from his home soil, the fresh growth of bark keeps record of the wonders he has seen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Ark: There is power yet in these old bones.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Bla: In the early days following his escape from academia, long before he assumed the title of Invoker, the young magus sought to test his growing skill by any means attainable. Like many other young talents burning for a taste of adventure, it was not long before he answered the call to war.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Blo: Banehallow often takes solace in the company of any fellow afflicted he might encounter in his wanderings. Not all, however, find the company of their own kind so agreeable.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Cha: The cruelties devised by the nobles of Devarque and their progeny remained novel long after N'aix's mind could no longer fathom the meaning of punishment.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Dar: The Dark Moon faithful consist of former scholars, laborers, orphans, and thieves. One may have served as magistrate of a city, another spilled blood as a warlord in the wilds. They have walked all imaginable paths to find Selemene. In her service, the trials and tragedies of the past matter not. They worship the Goddess together, guardians of the Nightsilver Woods.
'You gonna do what the little guy says, or we collectin' with interest?'
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Dem: These items were created in partnership with Alliance, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Dre: In the eyes of King Ostarion, the lives of his champions lost fighting to fuel the Wraith-Night rituals were merely his due tribute.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Fer: As the young orphan outgrew adolescence and his mastery of the Turstarkuri scrolls improved, he became eager to test his blades and begin his longed-for crusade to rid the world of magic, ultimately finding first opportunity as a volunteer in the failed defense of Bakhwarren.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Fir: All who see him shall know.
A kit's first tools must come from the remains of its prey.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Fra: 'Hey your plumage looks nicer than mine. Wanna trade?'
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Glu: Though the endless march of adventuring fools certainly disturbed the safety of her spiderlings, the constant supply of fresh treasure hunters did wonders for Arachnia's figure.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Gua: Though depictions of his body and form differ in the telling, the crackle of the Lightning Revenant's whip is known to all of the blessed few who have returned to life from the Narrow Maze.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Hun: Even the most skilled trackers may only hope to earn in a lifetime what Gondar claims on a single hunt.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Imp: Given enough gold and exposure to civilization, a troll's haughty nature lends itself well to indulging in a bit of finery.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Jia: Should the mob ever come for him a second time, Ethreain will be ready.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Kin: \"Do you mind if I slip into something from my 'Classics' period?\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Mec: Created in partnership with June, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Mot: Dim though it has become, the spark of life that holds fast within the heart of the Death Prophet blazes like a signal beacon in the endless darkness of death's abyss, beckoning all manner of feasting shades that long to taste the essence of the animate world.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Occ: Mundane prey attracts the uninspired predator. A distinguished huntsman, on the other hand, seeks a prize not bound by earthly coils.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Row: \"I'm all for a good riot. But never got on much with looters. They don't like my style. They complain about it, but their screams stop eventually.\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Roy: Though the carnage may go on without end, there are those alive still who can recall when it began. Ah, to be young and in the employ of the bloody King Brandalon once more.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Smo: In life, the warrior-poet's later-day accomplishments were even more impressive than those of his youth, as the wisdom of his years finally grew to match the purity of his martial arts.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Sou: There are those who view the servitude of Necro'lic as worse than any fate faced by those that fall under its ruthless gaze.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Tru: When Virga Truebark defied the Iron Princeling and sounded the Oakfall Horn, let it be known that Verodicia's favored son stood with her, fighting loyally by her side.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Ver:
'Neath vermillion plates
The shifting form
Of the star
Reborn.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loading_Screen_of_the_Wyr: The demasted figurehead of the Wyrmforge is just one of many lost relics gathered by the One for safe keeping and occasional good use.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lockjaw_the_Boxhound: Most boxhounds you're likely to come across would sooner eat you just for touching them, but all this little guy ever wants to do is play fetch.  His master never came home from battle, so if Lockjaw follows you home you should probably keep him.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lockless_Luckbox: Don't bother looking for your keys, because this chest doesn't need one! Our Lucky Lockless Chest contains one of a number of prized possessions that may be found only inside of it. So save your keys for a chest that needs them. You already got lucky!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lockless_Luckvase: No seal or key is needed to open this treasure, as it is already unlocked. This treasure contains individual items.

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Locuthi_Barding_of_the_Pe: The barding is lighter both in weight and in coloring, both necessary elements for survival in the dry wastes.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Locuthi_Mount_of_the_Peni: A mount is necessary elements for survival in the dry wastes.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Logitech_G_Challenge: An open tournament for all the best teams in Malaysia to compete for a total prize pool of $2,000 cash including gear from Logitech!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Logitech_G__Free_to_Play: LAN Centers all over India compete in Dota 2 for a total prize of 25,000 INR!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Logitech_G__Free_to_Play_: eSports Interactive Entertainment presents India's Biggest LAN Center Tournament with a grand prize of 50,000 INR!
India's Biggest LAN Tournament is back for a 3rd season. This open tournament takes place in a LAN environment where teams compete for the 130,000 INR Prize Pool.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Loners_Vanity: \"And why shouldn't I?\" Drow has been heard to say, to absolutely no one.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_LongFang_the_Grey_Blade: \"In the grip, the left hand must know Ardent Volition and the right hand must know Cultivated Grace. In this way the strike that follows bears both intentionality and respect. It is only the brute who strikes without these considerations.\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Long_Blade_of_Distant_San: The artisans of the eastern wastes are known for their ability to wrap golden beauty within sharpened practicality.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Longbeard_Dwarf_Engineer: Contains the Longbeard Dwarf Engineer for Sniper, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Longbow_of_the_Boreal_Wat: Only those attuned to frost may pull back the bowstring of the Tundra Walker.

Required Level: 8

Spell Lifesteal: 4%
Cooldown Reduction: 8%
Mana Cost Reduction: 8%
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_LootMarket_Invitational: 8 invited teams competing in a Double-Elimination bracket to claim the 3,000$ prizepool.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lord_of_Chronoptic_Synthe: Contains the Lord of Chronoptic Synthesis set for Leshrac, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lord_of_the_Scouring_Dune: This set contains all of the items in the 'Lord of the Scouring Dunes' set for Sand King plus a loading screen:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lord_of_the_Vicious_Plain: Contains the Lord of the Vicious Plains set for Centaur, including the Loading screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lords_Pauldron_of_the_Fla: Flameguard armor is functional, but also highly ornate. From their stations among the Inner Colonnade the Flameguard make their watch over the Holy Flame. This variation is the armor of a Flameguard commander.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Bow: With this bow, the fire of war is set.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Gauntlets: Fists of steel to go with your heart of fire.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Helm: Because most heat is lost from the head.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Set: Includes all of the items in the 'Lost Hills' set for Clinkz:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Shield: Carved from the oldest trees of the thousand-league wood, this shield will protect old bones from attack.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lost_Hills_Shoulder: A little padding to keep your bones warm.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lotus_Orb_Shell_Style_Upg: This International 2017 reward enables an upgraded shell to be unlocked for Hermes the Hermit Crab in the style menu.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lovebear:
The most important member of any team!

These Player Items are created in partnership with your favorite player, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Low_Skill_Cup_Season_1: Competition among beginners for the title of being the best among equals!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Low_Skill_Cup_Season_2: Competition among beginners for the title of being the best among equals!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lt_Squawkins_Rowboat_Upgr: This item enables the 'Rowboat' style to be unlocked on Lt. Squawkins through the style menu.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lt_Squawkins_Sailboat_Upg: This item enables the 'Sailboat' style to be unlocked on Lt. Squawkins through the style menu.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucid_Torment:
The dreamer's eyes are opened to a world of anguish.

Includes all of the items in the 'Lucid Torment' set for Bane, which can be upgraded with the 'Lucid Torment Style Unlock' granted to players who complete at least 40 stars on the Path of the Protector.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucid_Torment_Style_Unloc: This Fall 2016 Battle Pass reward enables an upgraded style to be unlocked on the 'Lucid Torment' set for Bane through the style menu. You can use this item multiple times to unlock styles on all of the items in the set.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucky_Alpine_Hat: A well worn hat adorned with a lucky feather and several blessed cholgar-teeth.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucky_Belly_Belt: Aggron says they found it just lying by the side of the road on a bandit they killed.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucky_Coin_Season_1: The first season of the tournament Lucky Coin. 16 teams of the CIS and Ukraine will compete for a prize of 3,200 rubles. TOP 3 teams will share the prize. TOP 3 team will be able to participate in free next tournament.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucky_Skull: A backpack, a cloak, the finest blanket you can steal, and a little souvenir for a discerning ruffian.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lucky_Tooth_Necklace: A necklace of rare leviathan's teeth.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Luki_ESport: The first season of the amateur tournament in which the best teams of Velikie Luki will meet in battle for the title of the champion!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lumberclaw: Countains the Lumberclaw set for Timbersaw, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Luminary_of_the_Dreadful_: Includes all of the items in the 'Luminary of the Dreadful Abyss' set for Morphling:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Luxuriant_ChinFoliage: \"Let those that would rule as Verdant Kings wear upon their brow horns sharpened with the wisdom of judgment and hang upon their chins a mighty symbol of their station.\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_LyaNagibe_Cup_Season_1: The tournament among beginners for the title of being the best among equals!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lycosidaes_Brood: With the relative safety of Mount Pyrotheos' lava tubes well behind them, the most vulnerable of Arachnia's offspring find shelter in a place few enemies would dare tread: on the back of the Broodmother herself.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lycosidaes_Favor:
Contains the Lycosidae's Favor and Spiderlings for Broodmother

Immortal items cannot be traded or marketed through The International 2018, but can still be gifted once. Only the bundle can be gifted.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lycosidaes_Spiderling: With the relative safety of Mount Pyrotheos' lava tubes well behind them, the most vulnerable of Arachnia's offspring find shelter in a place few enemies would dare tread: on the back of the Broodmother herself.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Lyraleis_Breeze: The only warning your enemies will receive will be the slight breeze that puffs their cheek as the arrow that kills them finds its mark.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MAGFest_14: MAGFest 14 attendees battle in the MAGFest LAN room for prizes and bragging rights!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MAX_League: Max League was created as an even ground so that talented newcomers can perform and achieve great things.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MD2_Malaysia_Brunei_Cup_S: Malaysia Dota 2 meets Brunei Dota 2. 16 teams from two countries compete to win MD2 Malaysia Brunei Cup Season 1.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MDL_Changsha_: MDL Changsha will see 12 top teams battle for glory and a big slice of prize money in China.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MFT_Dota_2_Indonesia: 32 Amateur Teams in Indonesia will play in this tournament, organized by the Dota 2 Indonesia Community.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_50000_Dota_2_Champion: Consuming this ticket will make you eligible for item drops while watching any MLG $50,000 Dota 2 Championship game.
MLG's first International Dota 2 competition will feature the world's best teams from Europe, China and North America competing for $50,000.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_Championship_Bundle:
MLG's first International Dota 2 competition will feature the world's best teams from Europe, China and North America competing for a growing prize pool starting at $50,000.
Included in this bundle:
* Scalehound Courier
* Stronghold HUD Skin
* Tethered Sentinel Ward
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_Columbus_Battle_Point: Use this item to increase the rate at which you earn <font color='#9da1a9'>Battle Points</font> to <font color='#9da1a9'>235%</font> until the end of MLG Columbus. Additionally, you will grant other players a stacking <font color='#9da1a9'>35%</font> bonus to their <font color='#9da1a9'>Battle Points</font> rate.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_NA_League_and_Full_Sa: The MLG North American Online League will have the best teams in North America vie for a chance to compete for $15,000 at Full Sail University.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_Scalehound: Found on the wild meadows of Druud, these vicious beasts are easily trained as beasts of burden and camp watchdogs.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_Stronghold: Even the mightiest offensive may fail against firm fortification.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_TKO: joinDOTA and MLG team up to present the MLG T.K.O.! This tournament features the top eight European and American teams compete for $60,000 in an innovative knockout format!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLG_World_Finals_2015: MLG World Finals in New Orleans, LA
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MLeS: Major League e-Sport is the South American Dota2 tournament for US $ 10,000
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MMR_Doubledown_Token: An item that is used for wagering your MMR.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MOL_Dota_2_Tournament: The top two teams of the MOL Dota 2 Tournament will represent Indonesia at the Game Master 2014 Malaysia.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_Gigabyte_2014_Finals: The completion of the year long event with all qualified teams gathering for an all expense paid trip to Manila for a 2 day event of non-stop Dota 2 action. Purchase the ticket to help increase the prize pool!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_SEA_Season_7: Mineski Pro Gaming League presents its seven season! Best teams from various countries in Southeast Asia will fly to Malaysia to participate in the Lan Grand finals in May 2015 for a total prize pool 50,000USD
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_SEA_Season_7_Bundle:
Mineski Pro Gaming League presents its seven season! Best teams from various countries in Southeast Asia will fly to Malaysia to participate in the Lan Grand finals in May 2015 for a total prize pool 50,000USD
	
	Bundle includes the Wild Tamer set for Beastmaster.
	
	25% of the proceeds of each sale contributes towards the MPGL SEA Season 7 prize pool!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_SEA_Season_7_Qualifi: Road to Malaysia start with MPGL SEA Season 7 Qualifiers. All teams in South East Asia will fight for the 11 slots in MPGL SEA Season 7 Final in Malaysia on May for 50,000USD
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_Season_6_SEA_Qualifi:
Mineski Pro Gaming League presents its sixth season! Teams from various countries in Southeast Asia will have their own qualifiers and the grand national champion will fly to the Phillipines to participate in the grand finals in November 2014!
	
	This ticket only gives you access to view games in the MPGL Season 6 SEA Qualifier.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MPGL_Season_6_Southeast_A: Mineski Pro Gaming League presents its sixth season! Teams from various countries in Southeast Asia will have their own qualifiers and the grand national champion will fly to the Phillipines to participate in the grand finals in November 2014! Bundle includes the Forest Faun courier!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSDT_Season1:
Metal Seinen is hosting its DOTA 2 tournament.
	12 teams will participate to win cool cash prizes in this tournament. Prizes: 1st: 10,000 PKR, 2nd: 5,000 PKR, 3rd: 3,000 PKR. This tournament will be the first of many tournaments by MS
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_BeatIT_RGN_League: South East Asia Qualifiers of the MSI Beat IT where teams compete for $5,000 total cash prizes plus travel and accommodation for the winner to the Global Finals in Taiwan in November.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_Beat_IT_2014: This year, MSI Beat IT includes Dota 2 and presents an opportunity to anyone out there to take part in the event through the open qualifiers and face off best Dota 2 teams in the world with a $44,000 prize pool! Each ticket purchased adds $1.50 to the prize pool!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_Beat_IT_Gosu_Cup_Asia: GosuCup Asia welcomes invites top Asian teams to compete alongside amateurs in the $2,000 MSI Beat IT GosuCup!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_Beat_It_Gaming_League: MSI Beat It Gaming League takes place in Indonesia where teams will compete for various prizes including cash and MSI hardware!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_Masters: The ESAU MSi Masters is a professional tournament compiling Australia's most talented players. Eight final teams will compete for the title and $3,000.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MSI_Southeast_Asian_Drago: The Southeast Asian Dragon Battle features the best teams in Southeast Asia competing for $3,000!. This event is sponsored by MSI and Adata.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MUFC_Pennant:
Show your support with a Team Pennant!
	
	Having a Team Pennant in your Armory will increase that team's Pennant Score which is shown during matches in Valve-supported tournaments, and it will make you eligible to receive item drops while spectating their live tournament matches. Pennants for the same team can be combined to increase their contribution to that team's Pennant Score.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MVP_Phoenix_Exhibition_Ma: MVP Phoenix plays a series of warm-up matches against top Southeast Asian and Chinese teams to prepare for The International 2014. These are free to spectate!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mace_of_Aeons: A thousand blows strike in a single moment stretched across the expanse of time, a death stroke that consumes eternity.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mace_of_the_Chosen: Weapons forged in the primal mists of the Font of Avernus may only be wielded by those the Font has chosen to defend it.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mace_of_the_Fissured_Soul: Ambient particle effects can be unlocked on this item using the Treasure Upgrade Infuser - Winter 2016.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mace_of_the_Wyrmforge_Sha: The demasted figurehead of the Wyrmforge is just one of many lost relics gathered by the One for safe keeping and occasional good use.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Dota2_League: This is the first Macedonian Dota 2 league where the best teams from Macedonia compete with each other for $2000!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Dota_2_Cup_#2: A Macedonian tournamentwhere all the Macedonian teams compete for a prize!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Dota_2_Cup_#4: Macedonian teams compete for items in the fourth season of the Macedonian Cup!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Dota_2_Cup_3: Macedonian teams compete for a prize in the third season of the Macedonian Cup!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Dota_2_Cup_5: Macedonian teams compete for items in the fifth season of the Macedonian Cup!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Macedonian_Elite_League: Top players compete in two divisions in the Macedonian Elite League for a prize!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mad_Moon_Summoning_Cup_Se: Over 32 teams from Europe are fighting for a prize.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maelstrom_Dota_2: An amateur Dota 2 tournament held in association with Excel 2015(Techno Managerial Fest of Govt. Model Engineering College, Kochi India.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mag_Gaming__First_Blood_: Mag Gaming presents First Blood ! An Indain Amateur Online Tournament featuring the upcoming Indian Teams battling out in a Single Elminiation format for a prize pool of Rs.30,000 !
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Magister_of_the_Narrow_Fa: Contains the Magister of the Narrow Fates set for Razor, including the loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Magnus: A collector's pin you can show off in your Steam profile.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Magus_Accord: Before the age of Gaster, even the most adept of mages would turn to flee with a burst of defensive magic when facing the close-quarters charge of a well-armed opponent.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Magus_Apex: The Sol Apex Incantation, forgotten for over nine thousand years, promised its caster the chance to touch the sun, bathe in its blinding glory, and harness its most scalding wrath. Only one would dare be so bold.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maiden_of_the_Slithereen_: \"Will you die to the Maiden, or to the Mistress?\" Pity whoever hears this final lyric.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mailed_Skirt_of_the_Drunk: When you're in your cups, this mailed skirt has your back.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Main_Dota_2_Champion_Tour: The Main Dota 2 Champion tournament is a double elimination format with prize pool RP 2.520.000.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Majesty_Of_The_Colossus__: In ages past, long before the settlements in the Azuran region were abandoned to ruin, the Odobenus forebearers harnessed the powers of rock, root, and iron to create fearsome guardians to watch over the tombs of their fallen legions even after the memories of their deeds had passed from the world. Little did they know the raw stone materials they'd utilized in one such creation also contained a powerful life force of its own, one not content to sit idly waiting for the threats of the outlands to arrive--one who would venture forth to stand watch over all lands in need of protection.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Majesty_of_the_Colossus: In ages past, long before the settlements in the Azuran region were abandoned to ruin, the Odobenus forebearers harnessed the powers of rock, root, and iron to create fearsome guardians to watch over the tombs of their fallen legions even after the memories of their deeds had passed from the world. Little did they know the raw stone materials they'd utilized in one such creation also contained a powerful life force of its own, one not content to sit idly waiting for the threats of the outlands to arrive--one who would venture forth to stand watch over all lands in need of protection.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Majesty_of_the_Eminence_o: Content for so long exploring the playground of the mortal realm, Akasha returns now to the dangerous Court of Ristul, where her star has fallen in her time away. But the Queen above intends to claim as well the throne below. Striking a bargain with an exiled demon prince, Akasha has seized a new measure of power, and her fiendish plans are at last set to begin.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Major_Allstars_Tournament: The Major Allstars tournament by Fallout Gaming will be open for SEA squads, with extensive qualifiers leading to the LAN finals in Malaysia with both eastern and western teams. The finals will take place in Kuala Lumpur in March 2015, with eight challengers battling for the initial $100k prize pool. 25% of the proceeds of each sale contributes towards the  Major All Stars prize pool!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Major_Allstars_tournament: The Major Allstars tournament by Fallout Gaming will be open for SEA squads, with extensive qualifiers leading to the LAN finals in Malaysia with both eastern and western teams. The finals will take place in Kuala Lumpur in March 2015, with eight challengers battling for the initial $100k prizepool
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Makeshift_Hornwood_Bow: A marvel of inventiveness, this makeshift bow proves that Windranger can kill you without fancy weapons.  In fact, all she needs is a few sticks bound together in the shape of a bow.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Makeshift_Sword_of_the_Re: A blade need not be made for combat to be useful in war.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malaysian_Amateur_Dota_2_: Amateur League for Malaysian Community to play competitively. At least 16 teams will play against each other every week for a prize pool of 100 MYR.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malaysian_Games_DOTA_2_to: Attention fellow Malaysian Dota 2 players of Melbourne, think you're better than the rest? Wanna put your skills to the test? Fret not, Malaysian Games 2016 proudly presents our first annual Malaysian Games Dota 2 Tournament, with a prize pool of over 650 dollars, join now.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malaysians_Hall_of_Fame_L: A league for  Malaysian's teams to play competitively for a prize pool of 1000 MYR! The top 4 teams will receive a slot for the next season.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malefic_Drakes_Hood_of_th:
Though he spurned most of the magics practiced by his naive captor, the inquisitive Netherdrake did take interest in his master's success in the realm of augmentations.
	
	This item was received after witnessing First Blood at The International 2017.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malice: Few things confer courage like the power of malice.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malicious_Efflorescence_S: Includes all of the items in the \"Malicious Efflorescence\" set for Spectre:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malicious_Sting: Contains all of the items in the 'Malicious Sting' set for Shadow Demon.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mallet_of_Magnificence: The go-to mallet for when your enemies absolutely, positively must be smited.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mallet_of_Sacred_Light: Some brethren proselytize without speaking a word; their sermons may be heard only in the ringing blows of the hammer.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Malu_Dota_Series_Finale: In 2013 we have hosted a total of four open Dota 2 tournaments. Now it's time to do the next step. While short cups are great for a lot of people, it was still our goal to make joinDOTA an even more stable place to compete for teams of any skill level.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mammoth_Lure: Once believed extinct, a small population of dwarf Mammoths can still be found on the isolated, northernmost peninsula of Icewrack.  They are shy creatures, not easily baited, but an offered stockpile of nuzzle-fruit will often entice them to approach.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mana_Pool: From a darkness unknown spills infinite power.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manado_Dota_2_League: Manado Dota 2 League is a local tournament from Indonesia that consist of 32 teams to fight for 6 million rupiah cash prize and the big 8 will be compete on LAN finals. This event is hosted by OurStory Gaming and WarStation, supported by IeSPA
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mancatcher_of_the_Crimson: The Crimson Cut-throat kept a wide assortment of ornate blades to do his work.  Once the contract was complete, Gondar helped himself.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mandate_of_the_Stormborn: There are some who believe the surge of power that comes to Raijin Thunderkeg's hands is a natural result of any expenditure of his power. But no power comes without struggle, even for a Celestial. Though his skill allows for an effortless appearance, it is through sheer will alone that Raijin is able to harness the excess forces that flow from each jolt of his abilities.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mane_of_the_Sunwarrior: These items were created in partnership with Alliance, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mango_League: Mango League is joint effort to create sustainable league system in South Korea by AquaTV, EDICH, BeginTV, and Minus9. Aimed at Korean amateur teams and Korean audience, Mango League brings the finest of Korean amateur teams, production, and casting.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manias_Mask: To wander the woods knowing you are alone, an orphan of those who birthed you, rejected by those who raised you, hidden from those who might give warmth and comfort... this is a path to madness.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manifold_Paradox:
Weapon evolves by earning points. Any match won using Phantom Assassin will earn you 1 point. Earning 40 points will upgrade the weapon to Level 2, and earning 100 points causes the weapon to reach its maximum evolution.

With a raspy cackle, the elder smith Craler swung the sword that his family had spent eleven generations to fold and forge. So sharp it was that, with a sound like tearing fabric, a rip in reality tore open. Through this rip, Craler recognized himself from moments before, holding aloft the very same coveted blade. Then, in a fit of greed and madness, he cut this earlier self down to seize the twin sword as his own. Too late, however, Craler felt a familiar wound, and was suddenly filled with the memory of being cut down himself...
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manifold_Paradox_Bundle: Contains the Manifold Paradox arcana for Phantom Assassin and the Gravestone emoticon.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manifold_Spear: A spear with three edges. It seems to reflect the light strangely.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manila_Major_2016: Who will emerge victorious? Witness the world's top teams battle at The Manila Major 2016.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manila_Major_Open_Qualifi: Witness teams from all around the world compete for a place at The Manila Major 2016 Regional Qualifiers.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Manta_Marauder: Contains the Manta Marauder set for Batrider, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Ancestral_Luck: The ogres of the elder days were said to be great builders and skilled artisans... by ogre standards.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Divine_Ascensio: Dashing and bold, this mantle helps Dragonus bear the great weight of Ascension's power.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Eldritch_Ice: The ice mage's robes became the Lich's tattered shroud. Superstitious subjects hammered spikes of sacred metal as a warning into the dead mage's skull, none suspecting that upon his resurrection he would wear the device as a cursed crown of domination.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Endless_Havoc: Heavy is the burden of unending war, yet many are its vicious pleasures.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Grim_Facade: When first reforming himself in the wake of Doom and Nevermore's umbral intervention, Shadow Demon gathered new parts to himself with little regard to form, so long as they were strong in function. Now, as his plans come ever closer to fruition and his strength nears its zenith, he chooses more deliberately a face fit to mete out the tragedies to come.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Hells_Ambassado: Suggestive of the robes of office of some infernal dignitary, the cape was an honorific bestowed on Lion by a grateful demon populace.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Mysteries: None know whose bones line mantle's fringe.  Every teller must ask unanswerable questions.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_Ultoria: This is not the first battle of import on this plane to necessitate the intervention of Barathrum at his master's behest.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Acolyte_of_: Travelling between dimensions, followers of Clasz require protection from the chill interstitial spaces.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Blackguard_: In the early days following his escape from academia, long before he assumed the title of Invoker, the young magus sought to test his growing skill by any means attainable. Like many other young talents burning for a taste of adventure, it was not long before he answered the call to war.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Blood_Coven: By the mantle of the Flayed Ones shall your enemies know you.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Blood_Moon: Banehallow often takes solace in the company of any fellow afflicted he might encounter in his wanderings. Not all, however, find the company of their own kind so agreeable.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Cinder_Baro: The Sorcerer King of Valhessi is but one title among many that the doppelganger Niyish has worn. Impersonating the Cinder Baron, the imposter led his forces on a disastrous military campaign, finally gaining an audience with the powerful Valhessian King during their surrender. Now, as the Inferno Keep melts into its volcanic foundations, this mantle is all that remains of the Cinder Baron's reign.
This item enables the upgraded texture to be unlocked on Axe's 'Mantle of the Cinder Barono' through the style menu.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Crescent_Mo: Plaid with moth wings and dressed with armour made from pure Moonsilver. A vestment like this is both rare and magical as it grants its wearer with the boon of increased agility.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Crested_Can:
Upon the shoulders of the cannoneer lie the fate of their fleet and fellows.

These Player Items are created in partnership with your favorite player, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Cruel_Magic:
The quest for knowledge oft leads down dark paths.

These Player Items are created in partnership with your favorite player, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Iron_Will: Against his shoulders does the world shatter.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Reef_Kyte_R: Astride a fintail reef kyte and protected against the crush by an enchanted helm, the moon rider serves as Selemene's champion and emissary in forging undersea alliances and keeping creatures of the deep at bay.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Sangstrath_: Rich in oral history, Ulfsaar's kin still celebrate the legends of the Sangstrath--ancient guardians of a fabled civilization and the first ancestors to settle the current lands of the ursine tribe after disaster befell their own.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Smoldering_: In life, the warrior-poet's later-day accomplishments were even more impressive than those of his youth, as the wisdom of his years finally grew to match the purity of his martial arts.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Stormcharge: Astride the focused storm, Disruptor stalks the boundaries of battle, ready to strike down his enemies and lead his tribe's return to a place of distinction and honor.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Truebark_Ad: When Virga Truebark defied the Iron Princeling and sounded the Oakfall Horn, let it be known that Verodicia's favored son stood with her, fighting loyally by her side.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mantle_of_the_Whispered_B: Not even Lanaya understands the true motives of the Hidden Ones, but the secrets they've revealed have more than earned her trust and loyalty. And if the whispers amongst her fellow temple adherents can be believed, soon a day will come when the hidden masters step forward to make the grand picture clear.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Marauder_Chieftan_of_the_: Contains the Marauder Chieftan of the Chaos Wastes set for Beastmaster, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Marauder_of_the_Chaos_Was: Contains the Marauder of the Chaos Wastes set for Beastmaster, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maraxiforms_Fate: If Clinkz must face the indignities of endless torment, the expired visage of that torment's origin would be made to bear witness as well.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maraxiforms_Fate_Bundle: Contains the Maraxiform's Fate and Fallen items for Clinkz
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maraxiforms_Ire:
Clinkz gifts the hellfire of Maraxiform's final breath to all who make threats against The Hoven.

Immortal items cannot be traded or marketed through The International 2018, but can still be gifted once.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mark_of_the_Blood_Moon: Banehallow often takes solace in the company of any fellow afflicted he might encounter in his wanderings. Not all, however, find the company of their own kind so agreeable.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mark_of_the_First_Hunt:
A kit's first tools must come from the remains of its prey.

This item can be upgraded with the 'Kit of the First Hunt Style Unlock' granted to players who complete at least 40 stars on the Path of the Saboteur.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mark_of_the_Mistral_Fiend: Includes all of the items in the 'Mark of the Mistral Fiend' set for Abaddon plus a loading screen and ability icons.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mark_of_the_Subtle_Demon: One must not balk at death.  One must learn to face all trials.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mark_of_the_Taunting_Swin: Spoon built a special sign to warn people away from where they intended to test the Swine cannon. Of course, they never got around to testing the cannon in the first place.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Markings_of_the_King_Rest: \"Do you mind if I slip into something from my 'Classics' period?\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Markswomans_Cap: Having a bad hair day?  No problem.  This snappy little markswoman's cap is stylish for all occasions.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MarsTV_Dota_2_League_2016: The 2016 MDL Autumn International Invitational tournament officially launches in September, boasting a prize pool of up to $250,000. The beautiful coastal city of Xiamen, China will host the top eight teams from China, Europe and the United States, starting off an exciting season!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MarsTV_Dota_Elite_Invitat: The first and second places from CN Qualifer for the International will face up four invited Chinese top teams in Huaxi, the top village in China.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Dark_Ferocity: In the bounty hunting business, a little intimidation can go a long way.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Distant_Sands: The heat of the eastern wastes is said to be extraordinary.  One must cover themselves appropriately.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Fury: Your face is masked but your fury won't be.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Inscrutable_Zeal: While not as sturdy as a proper dueling mask, this covering is better tuned to project words of power.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Metira: The enchanters of Metira could never abide human hands in possession of their artifacts. The few thieves who \"succeeded\" in liberating small baubles from their trove were hunted down and swiftly executed. For a Metiran master to gift a bespoke mask to Axia's ward Mirana -- an honor no other outsider had earned -- was a sign of gravest respect indeed.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Mortis: Each time Krobelus traversed beyond the veil revealed ever more complexities of the entities that call such a place home. While most seem unconcerned with the land of the living, some watch--and influence--the events of the material plane with deep interest.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_Petaluna: Though the priests of Dezun believe they alone possess the secrets of the ethereal shade, Dazzle's discovery of a race of insects in the lost jungles of Fellstrath capable of suckling energy directly from the Nothl Realm puts that claim to rest. But these creatures are inefficient with their feeding, and each puncture they create allows a bit of influence from the Nothl Realm to bleed into our own.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_a_Thousand_Faces: A ceremonial mask worn on special occasions. This must be a special occasion.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Chainbreaker: The cruelties devised by the nobles of Devarque and their progeny remained novel long after N'aix's mind could no longer fathom the meaning of punishment.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Confidant: Though the Gallants act for the most part in the open -- and indeed enjoy the renown that follows in their wake -- sometimes a cause must be taken up in which secrecy serves not only to safeguard the interests of the Gallants, but also to lessen the dangers facing those who need their protection.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Crimson_Cutth: The contract for the head of the Crimson Cut-throat was one of the most difficult that Gondar had ever accepted.  It was only natural that he'd keep a few souvenirs.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Divine_Sorrow: Has the Mask, Hood and Crown styles.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Freelancer: This old gladiatorial helm serves Sven well as he travels the land in search of honor and gold.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Hazhadal_Mage: After besting the young mages of his order, Nortrom put his newfound skills to use suppressing the godless outlaws of the Hazhadall Barrens, routinely making short work of their vaunted enthrallers.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Lightning_Lor: These items were created in partnership with Team Empire, who receive a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_ManySighted: On the Isle of Masks, death is said to have many watchful eyes.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Sangstrath_Fo: Rich in oral history, Ulfsaar's kin still celebrate the legends of the Sangstrath--ancient guardians of a fabled civilization and the first ancestors to settle the current lands of the ursine tribe after disaster befell their own.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Soul_Keeper: There are those who view the servitude of Necro'lic as worse than any fate faced by those that fall under its ruthless gaze.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_Tahlin_Watch: The crest of the Tahlin Watch sits upon the brow.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mask_of_the_ThiefScholar: Just as what is known must be learned, what is spoken must be thought.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masked_Fey_:
Noble by nature, Masked Fey overcame centuries of solitude to become guardian of the skies.

Includes alternate color styles.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masked_Fey_Courier_and_Sc: Includes Masked Fey courier and loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masks_of_Ancestral_Luck: The names of the twin leaders who once owned these masks have been lost to ignorance.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masque_of_Awaleb: Though the origins of Zharvakko's brand of arcanism are somewhat murky, and largely apocryphal, the exploits of the influential healer Awaleb are known far and wide. In an age of famine, disease, and unending violence, Awaleb concluded that the ailments of his people amounted to mere symptoms of a much greater sickness. So he began to turn his legendary cauldron towards the dark arts of harm. His people could always trust his word and prescriptions, but his greater act of service to them was a willing corruption of sacred vows in the name of protection, and the twisted legacy he would leave behind.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masque_of_Awaleb_Bundle: Though the origins of Zharvakko's brand of arcanism are somewhat murky, and largely apocryphal, the exploits of the influential healer Awaleb are known far and wide. In an age of famine, disease, and unending violence, Awaleb concluded that the ailments of his people amounted to mere symptoms of a much greater sickness. So he began to turn his legendary cauldron towards the dark arts of harm. His people could always trust his word and prescriptions, but his greater act of service to them was a willing corruption of sacred vows in the name of protection, and the twisted legacy he would leave behind.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Artificers_Hammer:
A powerful hammer used to extract Prismatic and Ethereal gems. Using a Master Artificer's Hammer will destroy the item it is used on.
	
	This tool can be used from the Item Details page, which can be accessed from the Armory by double-clicking on an item, or by right-clicking on an item and selecting Item Details.
	
	This tool is consumed on use.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Grim_Cut: The forked tip allows the wielder to pry back any armor the target may be wearing.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Mancatch: Designed to catch and hold the target, no matter which point is used.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Mask: The cloth is treated with oils and wax to stave off enemy poisons.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Shoulder: Built to deflect enemy weapons, the shoulder plates are carefully tailored to the wearer.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Shuriken: The blade end and grip are carefully balanced to sail through the air accurately, and with ease.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Assassins_Tails: The trailing cloth obscures the assassin's form and, in a pinch, can be used to thwart enemy blades.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Chocobo: Chocobos are no strangers to war. Though often recruited to carry soldiers into battle, their quick feet and strong backs also make them well-suited for carrying supplies to the front lines.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Gaming_Series_2015: Presented by QEON and CIPIKA PLAY, where amateur & professional teams fight for glory in the most anticipated & prestigious Dota 2 event in Indonesia.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Gaming_Series_Dota: This two-series tournament has the largest prize pool in Indonesia. The top teams from the region compete for the 100,000,000 IDR prize pool.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_League: Master League tournament teams Peru where beginners start looking for new challenges.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Necromancer: Contains the Master Necromancer set for Necrophos, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Master_Weaver_Set: Includes all the items in the \"Master Weaver\" set for Weaver.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Masters_Manila_2017:
We present to you The Masters, a Dota 2 tournament that will gather some of the best in the world.
	
	Organized by the Mineski-Events Team and supported by ESL, featuring a scale fitting for gladiators of the world stage, The Masters will surely change the competitive Dota 2 landscape as we know it.
	
	The first chapter of The Masters opens this May in the Philippines. Who will rise from the rest and be crowned the Manila Masters?
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Matt_Lange_Abstraction_Mu: Cinematic, glitchy atmospheres and hard-hitting rhythms by Matt Lange.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mattock_of_Distortion: One blow of this mighty mallet, and waves of time-warping distortion spread to erase his enemies from existence.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maw_of_Eztzhok: The thirst of Eztzhok became insatiable, and with each feast the demon's share of the Twins' tributes grew larger. As Eztzhok's gaping maw began to twist the visage of their loyal Hound, the Flayed Ones realized nearly too late that the reclamation of their Bloodseeker would not come without sacrifice.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maw_of_the_Devourer: From the World at the Rim, this staff is a weighty reminder of the howling void that waits for us all.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Maze_of_Anguish: To be wrapped in her wings is to be trapped in her web.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mazoku_League: Some of the best teams in South America face off to prove themselves as the best amateur team in the region.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meadows_Mercy: Though the forest itself may be neutral, this spear will bring a swift end to those who dare disturb the creatures who call it home.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meat_Dragger: Sometimes the meat won't go nowhere unless you drag it.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mecha_Boots_of_Travel_Mk_: Why rely on uncertain sorcery when an unstable machine can be just as dangerous? Painstakingly reconstructed from half-remembered schematics, the transdimensional technologies built into these boots is theorized to have caused the Violet Plateau Incident. Of course, that couldn't possibly happen again. Er, could it?
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mechalodon_Interdictor: Contains the Mechalodon Interdictor set for Gyrocopter, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mechanised_Pilgrim:
Includes all of the items in the 'Mechanised Pilgrim' set for Clockwerk plus loading screen and power cogs.

Created in partnership with June, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mechjaw_the_Boxhound: Between their experiments in transdimensional science, a pair of engineers in the facility atop the Violet Plateau designed a device to store and protect their most valuable valuables. Had those engineers not been eaten by indescribable horrors, they surely would have become rich!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Medium_Majesty_Of_The_Col: In ages past, long before the settlements in the Azuran region were abandoned to ruin, the Odobenus forebearers harnessed the powers of rock, root, and iron to create fearsome guardians to watch over the tombs of their fallen legions even after the memories of their deeds had passed from the world. Little did they know the raw stone materials they'd utilized in one such creation also contained a powerful life force of its own, one not content to sit idly waiting for the threats of the outlands to arrive--one who would venture forth to stand watch over all lands in need of protection.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meepo_Announcer_Pack:
Unearth some blue-collar wisdom and get multiple perspectives on every game in one convenient place with the Meepo Announcer Pack.
	
	Contains the Meepo Announcer and Mega-Kills Voices.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Axe:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the resonant booms of Axe.
	
	Available in English and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Bastion: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the smooth worldly tones of Bastion's narrator, also known as Rucks.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Bristleback:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the rough-and-tumble wit of Bristleback. Granted exclusively to owners of 2015's Compendium for The International.
	
	Available in English, Chinese, Russian and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Clockwerk:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the metal moxie of Clockwerk.
	
	Available in English, Russian, and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Crystal_Maiden:
This item replaces the Default Mega-Kills announcer with the cool sounds of Crystal Maiden.
	
	Available in English and Russian languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Dark_Willow:
This item replaces the default Mega-Kills announcer with Mireska's sly take on every game, helping ensure you never miss your mark in battle again.

Available in English and Chinese languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Darkest_Dungeon:
This item replaces the Default Mega-Kills announcer with the foreboding Ancestor from Darkest Dungeon, as voiced by Wayne June.
	
	Available in English.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Defense_Grid: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the upbeat wisdom of Defense Grid's very own General Fletcher.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Deus_Ex:
This pack replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the calm intensity of Deus Ex: Mankind Divided's Adam Jensen, played by Elias Toufexis.
			
	Created at Eidos-Montreal.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Fallout_4:
This pack replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the dry wit of everyone's favorite robotic butler, Mister Handy.
	
	Credits: Bethesda Softworks/Bethesda Game Studios/Stephen Russell
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_GLaDOS: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the withering sarcasm and passive-aggressive taunting of Portal's GLaDOS, science fiction's deadliest insult A.I.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Gabe_Newell:
On the eve of The International 2018, Kaci and SirActionSlacks hatched their most inspired idea yet--the Gabe Newell Mega-Kills Announcer. Determined to elicit the most bloodthirsty performance ever recorded, they lured Gabe into the studio... The rest is history.

This item replaces the default Mega-Kills announcer with the cruel taunts of Gabe Newell.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Juggernaut:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the enthusiastic shouts of the traveling warrior, Juggernaut.
	
	Available in English, Chinese, Russian, and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Kunkka__Tidehun:
This item replaces the default Mega-Kills announcer with a pair of naval nemeses here to bring the right kind of salt into each game.
	
	Available in English and Chinese languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Lina:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the fiery attitude of Lina.
	
	Available in English, Russian, and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Meepo:
This item replaces the default Mega-Kills announcer with some blue-collar Meepo wisdom and multiple perspectives on every game all in one convenient place.
	
	Available in English and Chinese languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Monkey_King:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with commentary from the legendary Monkey King.
	
	Available in English, Russian, and Chinese languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Natures_Prophet:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the wild cries of Nature's Prophet.
	
	Available in English and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Pirate_Captain: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the drunken antics of a scurvy-ridden Pirate Captain.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Pyrion_Flax: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the unique and unruly humor of Dota 2 satirist Pyrion Flax.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Rick_and_Morty: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the interdimensional mischief of Adult Swim's Rick and Morty.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Stanley_Parable: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the sardonically meta wit of the Narrator from The Stanley Parable.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Storm_Spirit:
This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the joyful exposition of Storm Spirit.
	
	Available in English, Russian, and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Techies:
This item replaces the Default announcer with the explosive enthusiasm of Spoon of Techies Demolitions.
	
	Available in English, Chinese, and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_MegaKills_Trine: This item replaces the Mega-Kills announcer with the soothing tones of Trine's tale-weaving narrator.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mega_Gamer_UTFPR_2015: An amateur championsip where the best teams from the south of Brazil fight for honor and almost $1000 in prizes!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mega_Greevil_Bundle: Contains a Mega Greevil courier, ward and loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mega_Greevil_Courier: Not all greevils are created equal. Once in a while, an egg will lay dormant through season after season, eventually hatching a greevil more hardy than its peers.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mega_Greevil_Ward: To some, greevil meat is a delicacy. It's never a bad idea to keep an eye out for predators!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Megalodon_Cup_Season_1: The Megalodon Cup features the top 8 teams from Brazil competing for a total prize of R$1,000!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Megalodon_Cup_Season_1__A: The Megalodon Cup features the top 8 teams from Brazil competing for a total prize of R$1,000!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Megalodon_Cup_Season_2: The top 16 teams in South America compete in the second seasno of the Megalodon Cup for R$1200! Bundle includes the Temple of the Sacred Memories HUD skin and loading screen!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Megalodon_Cup_Season_2_Ti: The top 16 teams in South America compete in the second season of the Megalodon Cup for R$1200! This ticket only gives you access to view games in the Megalodon Cup Season 2.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Megalodon_Starters_League: Teams participate in the first season of the Megalodon Starters League for cash and hardware prizes!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mei_Nei_Jade_Rabbit_Bundl: Contains the Mei Nei Jade Rabbit courier and loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mei_Nei_the_Jade_Rabbit: As eternal as the moon, Mei Nei fearlessly traverses the fields of battle in order to replenish the weary and wounded.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meister_Division: A mini tournament by The Meister Division event organizer with. Supported by AccentlTV. There are a rising stars amateur teams who agains each another to be number one at Indonesia.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meister_Dota_2_Captain_Dr: Meister Dota 2 Captain Draft Tournament is a Dota 2 Captain Draft Competition between 64 teams in the region competiting for a prizepool of over $700.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meister_Series_League: A mini tournament by The Bomb Squad Esports event organizer with prize pool 3.000.000 IDR, Supported by AccentlTV and The Wolf. There are a rising stars teams who agains each another to be number one in Indonesia.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mentor_of_the_Artif_Conve: Contains the Mentor of the Artif Convert set for Dark Seer, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mentor_of_the_High_Plains: Contains all of the items in the 'Mentor of the High Plains' set for Ember Spirit plus loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meranth_Dragoon: Contains the Meranth Dragoon set for Sven, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Meranth_Executioners_Blad: A single edged blade perfect for quickly removing heads. Or legs. Or arms.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Merciless_Spear: Built to strike into the core of an adversary, and tear it apart when withdrawn.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mercurials_Call:
Across time and space, the Spectre known as Mercurial has struggled to be understood. Now the full nature of her violent wrath can be heard.
	Granted exclusively to owners of the 2014 Compendium for The International.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Merry_Wanderers_Brush: Beneath the magic moonless night sprout sights rare-seen by mortal man: the swaying sweep of faerie flight unfurls to gorgeous shimmering span. And from this beauteous wonder light of shifting hue there might be spied, yet those who seek such perilous views may oft then find their lives denied.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Metal_Horns: In a time long forgotten, a grateful king once gifted the Prophet these horns as thanks for aid of the forest.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mexican_Cup: The top teams from Meixco are invited to prove they are the top team from the region.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Midas_Club_Elite: Midas Club Elite is a in-house developed for Brazilian community that have expanded over America. Featuring players with 5.5k+ MMR playing CM mode to fight for the 1st play on the ladder.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Midas_Club_Elite_Season_2: Midas Club Elite is a in-house developed for Brazilian community that have expanded over America. Featuring players with 5.5k+ MMR playing CM mode to fight for the 1st place on the ladder.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Midas_Club_Open: Midas Club Open is the entry league for Midas Club Elite. All players welcome to start to learn more about captains mode and leagues.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Midas_Knuckles: Midas has long been considered Alchemy's most successful practitioner. Seeking to address the incredible costs of war, he developed a series of gauntlet prototypes to be worn by revered knights of the kingdom, which were capable of minting coin with every strike.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Might_of_the_Galloping_Av: Contains the Might of the Galloping Avenger set for Magnus, including the Loading Scren
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Might_of_the_Old_World: A helm forged of enchanted alloys deep in the Astral plane, so that Elder Titan might better channel his Sprit and control both aspects of his broken soul.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Might_of_the_Slithereen_K: With this sword, truly, no Slithereen may fail.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mighty_Boar: This boar has a crazed look in his eye. Is it distrust? Madness? Or does he just want to eat your tangos.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Milan_Dota_2_League: The first season of the Milan Dota 2 league.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Militant_Cup_Season_1: The first season of Militant Cup series. 32 teams from CIS will compete each other. The winner will receive prize money upon victory!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mind_Piercer_of_the_Preda: Nyx's words enter the mind with great subtlety.  His horn enters the mind with considerably less subtlety.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mineski_ProGaming_League_: Mineski-Events Team proudly presents the 7th season of the Mineski Pro-Gaming League. Witness intense Dota 2 action as teams from all over the Philippines battle for the right to be named as the best in the country and a share from the initial prize pool of PHP 840,000.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mineski_Pro_Gaming_League: MPGL returns for the eighth season to gather the best teams in Philippines. Who will Rise from the Rest?
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Miracle_Tournament_Season: 32 Indonesian amateur teams will compete each other for 3.200.000 IDR Prize pool!!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mirana_of_Nightsilver: Bound by oath and honor to serve the needs of something larger than herself, Mirana of Nightsilver ranges far from home to defend the secrets of the temple she loves. In a world of twisted enemies and complex friends, she trusts in her bond with the fearless Sagan, and in the aim of her ever-ready bow.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mischief_of_the_Fae_Forag: Contains the Mischief of the Fae Forager set for Dark Willow, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mischievous_Dragon: Contains all of the items in the 'Mischievous Dragon' set for Puck plus a loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mistblade: Forged in the Font of Avernus, and filled with a dark thirst.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mistbreaker: Second of the three house blades of Avernus.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mistral_Braid: The wind that gently tousles her locks, gives unmatched flight to Windranger's arrows.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mistress_of_the_Long_Nigh: Contains the Mistress of the Long Night set for Death Prophet
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mistress_of_the_Slitheree: \"My Mistress, your Master,\" sings Naga as her enemies bow, never to rise.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mnemonus_Arcanus_Set: Includes all of the items in the 'Mnemonus Arcanus' set for Invoker:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Modestly_Braided_Beard: Even for the Avatars of Immortals modesty is sometimes called for.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mok: One of the wildest beasts of the escaped menagerie that ran amok during the fall of Slom, this wily mandrill took Mok for his name, thinking the citizenry's cries of warning were a herald of his arrival.  Now he puts his mischievous nature to good use, wading into any chaotic situation in order to bring you what you need.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moldering_Mask_of_Ka: Includes custom particle and custom ability icon.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Molokau_Stalker: Contains the Molokau Stalker item set for Venomancer
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Molotov_Cocktail_of_the_D: 'You gonna do what the little guy says, or we collectin' with interest?'
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Molten_Claw: In a rush to lay his enemies down, Axe burst into a forge to scrounge for suitable armor. What he found was still fresh from the fire, which suited Axe just fine. Includes ambient particle.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Molten_Fracture: Doom's power has shattered this blade.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Molten_Genesis: It takes a truly special bow to be wielded by fingers of flame.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Monarch_Bow: A relic from a hegemony long since passed, the Monarch rewards those who value lethal precision and skill over blunt force. As graceful in action as at rest, it complements perfectly the coolest of heads under the deadliest of circumstances.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Monarch_of_the_Sapphire_G: Long ago, before Nature's Prophet's seed was made to sprout, Verodicia imbued a sapphire gem with a spark of her essence, meant to be left behind in the wastes of a war-torn land so that the cycle of life might sooner return to a place bereft of it.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Monkey_King_Announcer_Pac:
This pack replaces the Default announcer and Mega-Kills announcer with the legendary musings of the Monkey King.
	
	Available in English and Chinese.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Monstrous_Reprisal: Contains all of the items in the 'Monstrous Reprisal' set for Riki plus loading screen, ability icons and an autograph. These items were created in partnership with VeRsuta, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Montenegrin_National_Leag: The third edition of Montenegrin National League will once again host the 24 best teams from our country who will compete for national trophy and prize pool that is going over 2500 euros. From November to April we will be witnessing clashes of the best teams in Montenegro so don't miss your opportunity to support your kings of Montenegro.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Montenegro_National_Leagu: Montenegro National League is the first professional Dota 2 league in Montenegro organized by Montenegro E-Sports Association. The best teams from country will compete for the championship and prizes!
Another season of Montenegro National League is coming with bigger and better prize pool. Who will become new masters of Montenegrin Dota 2 scene?
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Monty: A sophisticate vagabond of the highest order, Monty would look down his nose at you if he had one.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moon_Griffon:
On a night of a crescent moon, Mirana found a griffin cub in the maze of Nightsilver woods. Now the strange little beast is eager to serve his mistress.

This item includes custom Leap sound, idle and loadout animations.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moon_Rift: Contains all of the items in the 'Moon Rift' item set for Mirana plus loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moon_Rift_Style: Has two styles, Mask and No Mask
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moonfall: When Nightsilver Wood was yet but a thicket, a shard of stellar origin fell. Around this holy landing was built the Shrine of Selemene, and the shard itself fashioned into the most sacred of arms possessed of the order of the Dark Moon.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moonshard_Overgrowth: Contains the Moonshard Overgrowthset for Treant, including the Loading Screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Morbific_Provision: Contains the Morbific Provision item set for Witch Doctor
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Morcant: This pale creature found its way down the starlight path as if it heard its future mistress calling.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Morokai_Emoticon: Unlocks the Mo'rokai emoticon, awarded to players who have won 50 Wrath of the Mo'rokai matches.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Moroks_Mechanical_Mediary: Don't let its metal form deceive you: this contraption is more magic than machine. Fashioned by the Mad Mage Morok who was far too lazy to carry his own spell books and far too cheap to retain hirlings.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mortar_Forge: Contains all of the items in the 'Mortar Forge' set for Clockwerk plus a loading screen.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Most_Wanted_Tournament:
64 teams of Indonesia will fight for IDR 3.000.000. 
	Presented by Want3D
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mountain_Splitter: Usually used only by the Sagesmiths of Vuur, the stone antlers of the Murex elk are one of few tools capable of grasping the burning heartflint of the Vuurcrag mountains.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mountain_Trail_Challenge: The MTC is a proffesional tournament in which some of the best teams known will be invited to compete against each other.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mournful_Reverie: For one who has lost so much, a trickle of memory soon becomes a torrent of anguish.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mousesports_Pennant:
Show your support with a Team Pennant!
	
	Having a Team Pennant in your Armory will increase that team's Pennant Score which is shown during matches in Valve-supported tournaments, and it will make you eligible to receive item drops while spectating their live tournament matches. Pennants for the same team can be combined to increase their contribution to that team's Pennant Score.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Muh_Keen_Gun: Not content to kill things one bullet at a time, Sniper commissioned the best gunsmith in the land to construct him a firearm worthy of his talented trigger finger.  Lovingly designed and crafted with all the skill and attention to detail befitting a master smithy of the keen, the weapon that resulted is truly one for the ages.  It's a bit on the heavy side, true, but not when balanced against the weight of corpses it will produce.  Hernia not included.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mulan_girls_team_league: A series of various events held in the Mulan girl’s team league.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mulctant_Pall: In the eyes of the Demon Witch, those blessed with arcane power are but mere subjects, called upon to tithe their life's force in service of the hell-bent king.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mulctant_Pall_of_the_Crim: In the eyes of the Demon Witch, those blessed with arcane power are but mere subjects, called upon to tithe their life's force in service of the hell-bent king.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Murder_of_Crows:
Shoulda' kept your beak out of this.

These items commemorate the release of Valve's documentary, Free to Play, and were created in partnership with Dendi, who receives a portion of every purchase.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Murrissey_the_Smeevil: It is rare to find a smeevil far from the warmth of the forge to which it's bound, for they thrive on the affectionate cuffings and curses of their sworn smith. But the lure of a free tortoiceros ride compelled the smeevil Murrissey to break every oath...
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mysterious_Egg: A hard, scaled egg that seems to be alive and almost ready to hatch. It hungers for the magical energies contained in Diretide essences. What comes out will be determined by the type and amount of magic the egg consumes.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mysterious_Vagabonds_Conc: Although some travelling shaman have been rightly accused of selling colored water as if it were a certain cure for all ills, Rhasta makes no such claims and has never charged so much as a pence for a swig from this bottle. In fact, no one but Rhasta may drink from it. The Shadow Shaman's brew is certain death to anyone but its maker.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mysterious_Vagabonds_Hat: \"A shaman must take good care of his skin!\" Rhasta's master instructed. \"Therefore, always wear a hat to keep off the sun, and no less the evil influence of the moon.\" And then the old man always broke into laughter. \"And if you believe that, I have a bag of herbs here that will confer infinite wealth and immortality.\"
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mysterious_Vagabonds_Pack: His old master said, \"Be clear what you are about, for these simple village folk read menace and evil intent into poor communication.\" Therefore Rhasta created a simple visual menu of the services he offers, and wears it in plain sight.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mysterious_Vagabonds_Wand: A final twist of the serpent completes Rhasta's disguise, in case he is travelling incognito. It must be admitted that sometimes he wields it just because he likes the companionship.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Mystic_Instruments_of_Tan: This bundle contains all of the items in the 'Mystic Instruments of Tang-Ki' set for Shadow Shaman plus a loading screen:
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NACDEC: The Chinese Dota Elite Community invades North America! This in-house league lets players compete every 2 weeks in competitive Dota 2!

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NADota_Elite_League_Augus: The most talented players in North America compete in the classic inhouse league format for four weeks.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NADota_Elite_League_Seaso: NADota Elite League returns for its second season! The most talented teams in North America compete in the classic league format for eight weeks, culminating in a 4-team double elimination all-star tournament. $3,000 prize pool, 400+ games guaranteed. Hosted by IXDL. Broadcast by NEO Dota.
The most talented players in North America compete in the classic in-house league format.

NESO 4th National E-Sports ShenZhen Open Tournament- Galaxy Battles. 
	Offering a base prize pool of USD150,000 with 4 invited teams and 4 teams qualifying from the global qualifiers.
	
	A premier tournament exclusively brought to you by NESO, Purpose Win, Zeno and Fallout Gaming.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NFCups_Season_1: 32 amateur teams from Russia and CIS countries will fight for the first place and the title of NFCups Champions

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NGA_Master_League: NGA Dota2 Master League is a community-based tournament presented by National Geographic of Azeroth, the most prestigious gaming forum of China, always devoted to native game-stars cultivation and E-sports promotion. All Dota2 Elite players and teams nationwide will have intensive online competition
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NGT_Season_4: Featuring skilled semi-pro teams across Europe and North America, NeoN GuilD Tournament is back once again. Who will emerge victorious?
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NHK_League_Season_One: Top teams of NHK will fight for first place.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NN_Dota_2_League_Season_2: The second season of NN Dota 2 league will gather many teams from CIS, which will compete for a cash prize pool.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NN_Dota_2_League_Season_3: The third season of NN Dota 2 league will gather many teams from the CIS, to compete for a cash prize pool.

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NRS_GAMING_ONLINE_TOURNAM: 1st Online Tournament By NRS GAMING Where team will compete for a prize of 1.500.000 Rupiah
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NURE_Challenge_for_Studen: A league open to all students in Kharkov
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NYC_Cruise_Cup: KeyTV is bringing Esports to a whole new level, taking the dota2 competition to a cruise ship. 4 teams will compete on the deck and it will be a battle you have never seen.

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_NaVis_Weaselcrow: Fur and feather, beak and fang, Weaselcrow is just the thing!

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Nails_in_the_Mad_Harveste: If there's a better way to keep a shoulder together, I ain't heard it.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Name_Tag:
Use this tool to give an item a custom name.
	
	This tool can be used from the Item Details page, which can be accessed from the Armory by double-clicking on an item, or by right-clicking on an item and selecting Item Details.
	
	This tool is consumed on use. Custom names can be removed without using a Name Tag.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Nanyang_Championships: Nanyang Championship is one of the largest DOTA2 tournaments held in SEA, hosted by KeyTV. With a base prize pool of USD200,000 , this tournament will see 10 of the top DOTA2 teams across the globe meet in Singapore.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Nanyang_Championships_Sea: Nanyang Championships Season2 is back! There will be 8 of the best professional DOTA2 teams in the world coming to Shanghai to compete from July 6th to 10th.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Narcissistic_Leech: Contains the Narcissistic Leech set for Pugna, including the Loading Screen
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_National_Esports_League: 32 teams will compete in the first season of the National Esport League in the Dota 2 Super Cup for $250!
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Nature: In the verdant spring grows deep-rooted strength.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Natures_Grip: A well-seasoned staff, suited to the hoary wisdom of a woodland prophet.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Natures_Outcast_Horns: Ever in bloom are the horns of the wandering prophet.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Natures_Prophet_Announcer:
This pack replaces the Default announcer and Mega-Kills announcer with the stern voice of Nature's Prophet.
	
	Available in English and Korean languages.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Natures_Shortbow: Short in size, but long on killing power, this little bow is an ideal weapon for dispatching overconfident enemies.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Naval_Mine: When it fell to the depths and smashed a favorite coral bed, the Tidehunter swore to reunite the device with its owner.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Necklace_of_Scarlet_Raven: The sacred bird wheels above the altar of the Flayed Twins.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Necklace_of_the_Jiang_Shi: Should the mob ever come for him a second time, Ethreain will be ready.
Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Necklace_of_the_Wildwings: The Wildwing are fierce and territorial, but they more than tolerate Enchantress in their realms: They welcome her.

Tokens.DOTA_Item_Desc_Open_ReSF_Cup_2016_: Open ReSF Cup 2016 is your best chance to start professional carrier as a e-Sport player. Fight your way from online qualifiers to Grand Final, which would be conducted in Moscow in October 2016.
